snippet.title: Romeo S3 - Full Movie | Palak Tiwari, Thakur Anoop Singh | Pen Movies | New Hindi Movie 2025
snippet.description:
Romeo S3, directed by Guddu Dhanoa and produced by Pen Studios and Wild River Pictures, is an adrenaline-fueled Hindi action thriller set in the underworld of Goa.
Thakur Anoop Singh stars as DCP Sangram Singh Shekhawat, a fearless cop who goes undercover to dismantle a dangerous drug cartel while uncovering a sinister virus-linked conspiracy.
Opposing him is Palak Tiwari’s investigative journalist, Tanu, whose dogged pursuit of truth pulls her into Sangram’s high-stakes mission.
Packed with explosive fight scenes, high-speed chases, and larger-than-life stunts, the film delivers classic masala action in a bold, cinematic.
While praised for its sheer energy and punchy performances, critics note the storyline sometimes leans on predictable tropes and formulaic twists.

snippet.title: Stranger Things 5 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
Every battle has led to this.

More about Stranger Things 5:
The fall of 1987. Hawkins is scarred by the opening of the Rifts, and our heroes are united by a single goal: find and kill Vecna. But he has vanished — his whereabouts and plans unknown. Complicating their mission, the government has placed the town under military quarantine and intensified its hunt for Eleven, forcing her back into hiding. As the anniversary of Will’s disappearance approaches, so does a heavy, familiar dread. The final battle is looming — and with it, a darkness more powerful and more deadly than anything they’ve faced before. To end this nightmare, they’ll need everyone — the full party — standing together, one last time.

snippet.description:

Is vaar gall sirf beats di nahi – ae taan Sabba Da Lanter ae, jisnu vekh ke poora pind hi nach paeya! 🔥

Credits :

Speed Records Presents
Song - Village Flow
Singer/Composer/Lyrics - Sabba
Music - JayB Singh
Direction/Concept?Screenplay : Sahil Sharma
Presentation : Meeru

Editor : HC Edittz

Digital Managed By Scope Entertainment

Reel Promotions By Scope Digital
Label - Speed Records

Lyrics :
Ni baitha mai trakki de mathe ch jhanda gaddke
Ni utte nahio aaya thalle kise de vi laggke
Oh hun mera changa aaya kehnde pair chhad gya
Ni jehde maade time ch gye si hath chhadke
Oh lanka nahio dhayi bhave bheti aa harek de
Ni mere saale kinne hi jo bahre pye aa hate de
Ni bahoteya de rang udd janda kude face to
Ni charno da dohta baitha gaddi vich vekhke
Ho vekhi mardanya eh rang kartar de
Oh aap mar jande jehde doojeya nu maarde
Ho bahn jihdi fadi hove neeli Chhatt wale ne
Ni kitho sutt hona a laler nehri taarke
Oh chhetti hath aunde nahio uchiya udariyaan
Ni reejh na pugaiye asi vair nale yaariyan
Oh vairi voori vekhke badak maar dyidi
Ni kudi jandi vekh kde whistlaan ni maariyan
Ni gabhru rakaane bebe bapu ji to baahre na
Na saade kolo vaade hone lagne ve laare na
Ni tere kolo main vi tere maa-pe charwaune na
Te mere kolo ranjhe wangu pashu jaane chaare na
Na dil to greeb bhave bhute na ameer ni
Aa jehde nal bhai kathi kri na mandeer ni
Ni susti na nede tede mitran de laggdi 
Ni 24 ghante lor vich rehnda ae sareer ni
Ni bhaiyan te yakeen security jeyo z te
Ho bade dil lutte akh mittraa di red ne
Ho dabb nal lgga jo rakaane 30 bore da
Flower bna dewe bhaida eh forehead te
Na nimm jehe lot aune mitthi teri talk to
Na pighluga dil eh jwaani teri hot to
Dass fer sher da ni rutba ki reh gya
Je oh vi gya pattya rakaane cat walk to
Oh zindgi nu reejha nal maande aa baithke
Koi chakkr ni meeru bai khada jado back te
Ho asi befikre 9 10 vje sojiye
Ni sathon gallan adhi raat honiya ni chat te
Ni chattya ni kde v yaara ne billo thukk ke
Oh jo vi kita shar-e-aam kreya ni lukk ke
Oh Kayi saale raula pake kehn asi ki aa
Te sara kujh dssya ae mittra di chupp ne
Jo tappde aa salya nu shittra di ghaat ni
Oh fer vekhi baith jaane sara chupp chaap ni
Ohh kehnde ne ke saade naalo vadda koi vaily ni
Te Dhaai saah ne ch*** de utte bhora maas ni
Neet saaf rabb ne vi kujh ni lakoya kude
Tension ni len koi dinda bai saroya kude
Dhannwaad karda va saareya da dil to
Haaye pauna si punjab kattha lentar te hoya kude
Ho dunia ta jitti baitha hun kithe haar da
Jhool jhool ture kude pota jagtar da
Oh jihna hun takk aukh vich hi aa kattli
Ni maapeya nu geda mai lwauna ik bahar da
Ho guru ghar jaake bhala sareyaa da mangda
Ho adhi cho vi adhi cheej doojeya na vand da
Ho mai ni kehnda rabb bahla deyi jawe menu
Jinna mera banda onna hi ohto mangda

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat II | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's called Mortal Kombat (II).
Mortal Kombat II – only in theaters and @imax October 24. #MortalKombatMovie #FilmedForIMAX 

From New Line Cinema comes the latest high-stakes installment in the blockbuster video game franchise in all its brutal glory, Mortal Kombat II.  This time, the fan favorite champions—now joined by Johnny Cage himself—are pitted against one another in the ultimate, no-holds barred, gory battle to defeat the dark rule of Shao Kahn that threatens the very existence of the Earthrealm and its defenders.

Karl Urban stars as Johnny Cage, alongside Adeline Rudolph, Jessica McNamee, Josh Lawson, Ludi Lin, Mehcad Brooks, Tati Gabrielle, Lewis Tan, Damon Herriman, with Chin Han, Tadanobu Asano as Lord Raiden, Joe Taslim as Bi-Han, and Hiroyuki Sanada as Hanzo Hasashi and Scorpion.

Director Simon McQuoid returns to helm the follow up to his explosive 2021 cinematic adventure, from a screenplay by Jeremy Slater, based on the videogame created by Ed Boon and John Tobias.  The film is produced by Todd Garner, James Wan, Toby Emmerich, E. Bennett Walsh and McQuoid, and executive produced by Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Slater and Lawrence Kasanoff.  

Joining McQuoid behind the camera are director of photography Stephen F. Windon, production designer Yohei Taneda, editor Stuart Levy and costume designer Cappi Ireland, with casting by Rich Delia and music by Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents an Atomic Monster/Broken Road Production, a Fireside Films Production, Mortal Kombat II.  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theaters and IMAX® across North America on October 24, 2025, and internationally beginning 22 October 2025.

snippet.title: Mr. Truth | Episode 11 | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
This is a reflection of a disturbing reality unfolding in our land. In recent times, our own people have watched silently, and in some cases, even enabled,  the rise of certain outsiders who have crossed every line of decency, safety, and respect.
Based on true incidents reported in our state, on how some non-locals, once welcomed as workers and settlers, have now turned aggressive, entitled, and even violent — involved in molestation, assault, and intimidation of local men and women. The worst part? A few local gundas and power-hungry individuals are protecting them for money and personal benefit.
This video is not against any community and does not target or generalize all non-locals but it raises a serious question, How long will we stay silent when dignity, safety, and respect are at stake? So this is against those who abuse the hospitality and silence of the land they live in. It’s against those who disrespect our mothers, threaten our youth, and treat the locals as second-class in their own homeland.
Not all are bad, but ignoring the bad ones is dangerous.
Let’s not protect criminals. 
Let’s protect our community. Lets save our land.

localized.title: Mr. Truth | Episode 11 | Dreamz Unlimited
localized.description:
This is a reflection of a disturbing reality unfolding in our land. In recent times, our own people have watched silently, and in some cases, even enabled,  the rise of certain outsiders who have crossed every line of decency, safety, and respect.
Based on true incidents reported in our state, on how some non-locals, once welcomed as workers and settlers, have now turned aggressive, entitled, and even violent — involved in molestation, assault, and intimidation of local men and women. The worst part? A few local gundas and power-hungry individuals are protecting them for money and personal benefit.
This video is not against any community and does not target or generalize all non-locals but it raises a serious question, How long will we stay silent when dignity, safety, and respect are at stake? So this is against those who abuse the hospitality and silence of the land they live in. It’s against those who disrespect our mothers, threaten our youth, and treat the locals as second-class in their own homeland.
Not all are bad, but ignoring the bad ones is dangerous.
Let’s not protect criminals. 
Let’s protect our community. Lets save our land.

snippet.title: Inside India's BIGGEST Festival with 30 Lakh People! 🤯 (Pandharpur Wari)
snippet.description:
Pandharpur Wari 2025 – A Spiritual Journey with 30 Lakh Devotees

In this immersive documentary, we dive deep into the heart of the Pandharpur Wari. Here's what we explored:

🔸 30 Lakh+ People Walking for Days – A sea of faith marching towards Pandharpur
🔸 Lived Among the Warkaris – Visited and documented how people live in tents during the yatra
🔸 Witnessed the Sacred Ringan – A divine ritual where a riderless horse representing the soul of a saint runs through the crowd, symbolizing devotion and energy
🔸 Spoke to Warkaris – Heartfelt conversations with devotees who walk hundreds of kilometres out of pure devotion
🔸 Walked 10 km Everyday – Experienced the physical and emotional journey ourselves
🔸 Uncovered Mysterious Stories – Legends, miracles, and untold tales of the Wari
🔸 Revealed the Truth Behind the Name 'Vitthal' – An exploration into the meaning, history, and significance of Vitthal Mauli
🔸 Stories of Sant Tukaram & Sant Dnyaneshwar – And many other saints whose teachings guide the Warkari tradition even today

This is more than a documentary – it’s a glimpse into the soul of Maharashtra.

🙏 Jai Mauli!

snippet.title: Deepti Sharma Lead India Home |ENG W vs IND W | 1st ODI | Highlights | India Women’s Tour Of England
snippet.description:
India Women edged past England with a thrilling 4-wicket win in the 1st ODI at the Rose Bowl. England recovered from early blows to post 258 for 6, thanks to solid knocks from Emma Lamb and Nat Sciver-Brunt. In reply, Deepti Sharma’s composed 62 off 64 balls anchored India’s chase, supported by key contributions from Mandhana and Rodrigues. Despite tight spells from England’s bowlers, India held their nerve to take the lead in the series.

snippet.description:

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Farm Tour in Tamil | Steffi Ulagam
snippet.description:
In this vlog, we visited a farm in which we had planted some fruit trees a couple of years ago when we visited India. Those plants have grown up and have started producing fruits. While there are predominantly coconut trees, we were able to get some other fruit trees between them. Join us as we explore our small farm in India, enjoying the fruits of our labor with a delightful fruit harvest. We're picking mangoes, coconuts, and dragon fruit, savoring the taste of these homegrown fruits. 

I hope seeing these fruit trees kindled some desire in you for gardening and I hope you will also try to grow some plants. Hope you liked this week's vlog and see you next week with more interesting videos.

snippet.description:

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun.

#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. --------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: UK & Europe Trains Are Not What I Expected | Unscripted StandUp Comedy "Rant" by Rahul Dua | 2025
snippet.description:
Coming to 14 cities across UK & Europe in Sept'25 with my comedy special Allow Me! Tickets: https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour

Germany ka train system + UK ki train strike = Confused Indian traveler ka breakdown 😅. 
In this unrehearsed, unscripted, straight-from-the-heart stand-up bit, I talk about my chaotic Europe tour in 2023 - from Berlin to Munich, Birmingham to London - and how desi expectations just don't match European transport “efficiency”. 😤 I don't think I'd use "punctuality" and "German trains" in the same sentence again :P

No ACs in Europe, sweltering heat, trains that split mid-journey and UK’s legendary train strike — everything that could go wrong, did.
If you’ve ever traveled in Europe, struggled with Bahn systems, or faced sudden cancellations and delays — this one’s for you. Watch till the end for a real life example of "laut k buddhu ghar ko aaye". 

✈️ Have your own Europe travel disaster story? Drop it in the comments! Share it with your friends who are planning a Europe trip or don't stop talking about how good it was. 

Comment the city you have planned to visit and i'll share a tip or two about that city that no one else will. 

👉 Don’t forget to Like, Comment, Share & Subscribe for more travel rants and standup comedy! Next standup video coming in less than 2 weeks. 

#StandUpComedy #IndianInGermany #DesiTraveler #IndianComedianAbroad #TrainStrike #EuropeTravelFails  

Shot on 8th Sept 2023 in Köln, Germany
Shot by: Yours Truly and Mehtab Singh, on tour
Sound recording by: Yours Truly and Mehtab Singh, on tour
Editing and Grading by: Gaurav Bhatt ( /@gauravbhatt101)

snippet.title: अब बदल रहा है Monsoon का रास्ता! मध्य भारत में थमेगी बारिश, पूर्व में लौटेगा मानसून | Skymet Weather
snippet.description:
18 जुलाई से मध्य प्रदेश और बिहार में बारिश की गतिविधियां कम होना शुरू हो जाएगी। 19 जुलाई को बिहार, झारखंड, उत्तर प्रदेश, मध्य प्रदेश, पंजाब, हरियाणा, और दिल्ली सहित उत्तरी राजस्थान में बहुत हल्की बारिश की संभावना है। लेकिन 19 जुलाई को उत्तर पश्चिम बंगाल की खाड़ी में एक साइक्लोनिक सर्कुलेशन बनेगा। इसके प्रभाव से पश्चिम बंगाल, उड़ीसा और बिहार के पूर्वी जिलों में एक बार फिर बारिश शुरू हो जाएगी। यह बारिश की गतिविधियां फिर से मध्य भारत की तरफ आएंगी और मानसून को सक्रिय कर देंगी। पहाड़ों पर भारी बारिश का दौर जारी रहेगा। केरल में भारी बारिश और कर्नाटक तट पर भी मध्यम से भारी बारिश की संभावना है। मुंबई सहित महाराष्ट्र में बारिश कुछ हल्की पड़ जाएगी।

ko.title: 이제 몬순의 경로가 바뀌고 있습니다! 인도 중부에서는 비가 그치고, 동부에서는 몬순이 다시 나타날 것입니다. | 스카이멧 날씨
ko.description:
7월 18일부터 마디아프라데시와 비하르에서는 강우량이 감소하기 시작할 것으로 예상됩니다. 7월 19일에는 비하르, 자르칸드, 우타르프라데시, 마디아프라데시, 펀자브, 하리아나, 델리, 그리고 북부 라자스탄 지역에 매우 약한 비가 내릴 것으로 예상됩니다. 그러나 7월 19일에는 벵골 북서만에서 저기압 순환이 형성될 것으로 예상됩니다. 이 저기압의 영향으로 서벵골 동부 지역, 오디샤, 비하르 지역에 다시 비가 내리기 시작할 것입니다. 이 강우량은 다시 인도 중부 지역으로 이동하여 몬순을 활성화할 것입니다. 산악 지역에는 폭우가 계속될 것으로 예상됩니다. 케랄라에도 폭우가 예상되며, 카르나타카 해안 지역에는 중간 정도에서 강한 비가 내릴 것으로 예상됩니다. 뭄바이를 포함한 마하라슈트라 지역에는 비가 다소 약해질 것으로 예상됩니다.

id.title: Kini arah Monsun berubah! Hujan akan berhenti di India tengah, Monsun akan kembali ke timur | Cua...
id.description:
Mulai 18 Juli, aktivitas hujan akan mulai berkurang di Madhya Pradesh dan Bihar. Pada 19 Juli, hujan ringan diperkirakan terjadi di Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana, dan Delhi, termasuk Rajasthan utara. Namun, pada 19 Juli, sirkulasi siklon akan terbentuk di Teluk Benggala Barat Laut. Akibat pengaruhnya, hujan akan kembali turun di wilayah timur Benggala Barat, Odisha, dan Bihar. Aktivitas hujan ini akan kembali menuju India tengah dan mengaktifkan monsun. Hujan deras akan terus berlanjut di pegunungan. Hujan deras juga diperkirakan terjadi di Kerala dan hujan sedang hingga lebat di pesisir Karnataka. Hujan akan sedikit lebih ringan di Maharashtra, termasuk Mumbai.

18 जुलाई से मध्य प्रदेश और बिहार में बारिश की गतिविधियां कम होना शुरू हो जाएगी। 19 जुलाई को बिहार, झारखंड, उत्तर प्रदेश, मध्य प्रदेश, पंजाब, हरियाणा, और दिल्ली सहित उत्तरी राजस्थान में बहुत हल्की बारिश की संभावना है। लेकिन 19 जुलाई को उत्तर पश्चिम बंगाल की खाड़ी में एक साइक्लोनिक सर्कुलेशन बनेगा। इसके प्रभाव से पश्चिम बंगाल, उड़ीसा और बिहार के पूर्वी जिलों में एक बार फिर बारिश शुरू हो जाएगी। यह बारिश की गतिविधियां फिर से मध्य भारत की तरफ आएंगी और मानसून को सक्रिय कर देंगी। पहाड़ों पर भारी बारिश का दौर जारी रहेगा। केरल में भारी बारिश और कर्नाटक तट पर भी मध्यम से भारी बारिश की संभावना है। मुंबई सहित महाराष्ट्र में बारिश कुछ हल्की पड़ जाएगी।

it.title: Ora il percorso del monsone sta cambiando! La pioggia cesserà nell'India centrale, il monsone tor...
it.description:
Dal 18 luglio, le precipitazioni inizieranno a diminuire in Madhya Pradesh e Bihar. Il 19 luglio, sono previste piogge molto deboli in Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana e Delhi, incluso il Rajasthan settentrionale. Tuttavia, il 19 luglio, si formerà una circolazione ciclonica nel Golfo del Bengala nord-occidentale. A causa del suo effetto, le piogge ricominceranno a cadere nei distretti orientali del Bengala Occidentale, dell'Odisha e del Bihar. Questa attività piovosa si dirigerà nuovamente verso l'India centrale, innescando il monsone. Le forti piogge continueranno sulle montagne. Sono previste forti piogge anche in Kerala e piogge da moderate a intense sulla costa del Karnataka. Le piogge diventeranno piuttosto deboli nel Maharashtra, inclusa Mumbai. #Monsoon2025 #Monsoon #AggiornamentiMeteo #PrevisioniMeteo #SkymetWeather #Skymet #Meteo

pl.title: Teraz zmienia się trasa monsunu! Deszcz ustanie w środkowych Indiach, monsun powróci na wschód | ...
pl.description:
Od 18 lipca opady deszczu zaczną ustępować w Madhja Pradesz i Biharze. 19 lipca bardzo lekkie opady deszczu spodziewane są w Biharze, Jharkhandzie, Uttar Pradesz, Madhja Pradesz, Pendżabie, Harianie i Delhi, łącznie z północnym Radżastanem. 19 lipca w północno-zachodniej Zatoce Bengalskiej uformuje się cyrkulacja cykloniczna. Z tego powodu opady ponownie rozpoczną się we wschodnich dystryktach Bengalu Zachodniego, Orisy i Biharu. Ta aktywność deszczowa ponownie dotrze do centralnych Indii, aktywując monsun. Ulewne deszcze będą nadal występować w górach. Ulewne deszcze spodziewane są również w Kerali, a umiarkowane do silnych na wybrzeżu Karnataki. Opady deszczu staną się nieco słabsze w Maharasztrze, w tym w Mumbaju.

nl-NL.title: Nu verandert het pad van de moesson! De regen stopt in centraal India, de moesson keert terug naa...
nl-NL.description:
Vanaf 18 juli neemt de regenval in Madhya Pradesh en Bihar af. Op 19 juli wordt zeer lichte regen verwacht in Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana en Delhi, inclusief Noord-Rajasthan. Maar op 19 juli vormt zich een cyclonische circulatie in de noordwestelijke Golf van Bengalen. Door de gevolgen hiervan zal het opnieuw regenen in de oostelijke districten van West-Bengalen, Odisha en Bihar. Deze regenval zal zich opnieuw richting Centraal-India verplaatsen en de moesson activeren. Zware regenval houdt aan in de bergen. Ook in Kerala wordt zware regenval verwacht en aan de kust van Karnataka matige tot zware regenval. In Maharashtra, inclusief Mumbai, zal de regenval wat milder worden.

ja.title: モンスーンの進路が変わりつつあります！インド中部では雨が止み、モンスーンは東へ戻ります | Skymet Weather
ja.description:
7月18日からは、マディヤ・プラデーシュ州とビハール州で雨量が減少します。7月19日には、ビハール州、ジャールカンド州、ウッタル・プラデーシュ州、マディヤ・プラデーシュ州、パンジャブ州、ハリヤーナー州、そしてデリー（北部ラジャスタン州を含む）で非常に弱い雨が予想されます。しかし、7月19日には、ベンガル湾北西地域でサイクロン循環が発生します。その影響で、西ベンガル州、オリッサ州、ビハール州の東部地域で再び雨が降り始めます。この雨は再びインド中部に流れ込み、モンスーンを活発化させます。山岳地帯では大雨が続く見込みです。ケーララ州でも大雨が予想され、カルナタカ州沿岸部では中程度から激しい雨が予想されます。ムンバイを含むマハラシュトラ州では、雨量はやや弱まる見込みです。

fr-FR.title: La mousson change de direction ! La pluie cessera dans le centre de l'Inde et la mousson reviendr...
fr-FR.description:
À partir du 18 juillet, les précipitations commenceront à diminuer dans le Madhya Pradesh et le Bihar. Le 19 juillet, de très faibles pluies sont attendues dans le Bihar, le Jharkhand, l'Uttar Pradesh, le Madhya Pradesh, le Pendjab, l'Haryana et Delhi, ainsi que dans le nord du Rajasthan. Cependant, le 19 juillet, une circulation cyclonique se formera dans le nord-ouest du golfe du Bengale. Sous son effet, les pluies reprendront dans les districts orientaux du Bengale-Occidental, de l'Odisha et du Bihar. Ces précipitations se dirigeront de nouveau vers le centre de l'Inde et activeront la mousson. De fortes pluies persisteront dans les montagnes. De fortes pluies sont également attendues au Kerala et des pluies modérées à fortes sur la côte du Karnataka. Les pluies deviendront plutôt faibles dans le Maharashtra, y compris à Mumbai. #Monsoon2025 #Monsoon #WeatherUpdate #WeatherForecast #SkymetWeather #Skymet #Weather

pt-BR.title: Agora, a trajetória das monções está mudando! A chuva vai parar no centro da Índia, e as monções ...
pt-BR.description:
A partir de 18 de julho, as chuvas começarão a diminuir em Madhya Pradesh e Bihar. Em 19 de julho, chuvas muito fracas são esperadas em Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana e Delhi, incluindo o norte do Rajastão. No entanto, em 19 de julho, uma circulação ciclônica se formará no noroeste da Baía de Bengala. Devido a esse efeito, a chuva começará novamente nos distritos orientais de Bengala Ocidental, Odisha e Bihar. Essa atividade chuvosa retornará à Índia central e ativará as monções. Chuvas fortes continuarão nas montanhas. Chuvas fortes também são esperadas em Kerala e chuvas moderadas a fortes na costa de Karnataka. As chuvas se tornarão relativamente fracas em Maharashtra, incluindo Mumbai.

es-US.title: ¡La trayectoria del monzón está cambiando! La lluvia cesará en el centro de la India y el monzón ...
es-US.description:
A partir del 18 de julio, las precipitaciones comenzarán a disminuir en Madhya Pradesh y Bihar. El 19 de julio se esperan lluvias muy ligeras en Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana y Delhi, incluyendo el norte de Rajastán. Sin embargo, el 19 de julio, se formará una circulación ciclónica en el noroeste de la Bahía de Bengala. Debido a su efecto, volverán a llover en los distritos orientales de Bengala Occidental, Odisha y Bihar. Estas precipitaciones volverán al centro de la India y activarán el monzón. Continuarán las fuertes lluvias en las montañas. También se esperan lluvias intensas en Kerala y lluvias moderadas a intensas en la costa de Karnataka. Las lluvias serán algo ligeras en Maharashtra, incluyendo Mumbai. #Monzón2025 #Monzón #ActualizaciónMeteorológica #PronósticoMeteorológico #SkymetWeather #Skymet #ElTiempo

de-DE.title: Jetzt ändert sich der Monsunverlauf! In Zentralindien hört der Regen auf, der Monsun kehrt in den...
de-DE.description:
Ab dem 18. Juli nehmen die Regenfälle in Madhya Pradesh und Bihar ab. Am 19. Juli wird in Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttar Pradesh, Madhya Pradesh, Punjab, Haryana und Delhi sowie im Norden Rajasthans mit sehr leichtem Regen gerechnet. Am 19. Juli bildet sich jedoch im Nordwesten der Bucht von Bengalen eine zyklonische Zirkulation. Aufgrund ihrer Auswirkungen wird es in den östlichen Distrikten von Westbengalen, Odisha und Bihar erneut regnen. Diese Regenfälle werden sich wieder auf Zentralindien ausbreiten und den Monsun auslösen. In den Bergen wird es weiterhin heftig regnen. Auch in Kerala werden heftige Regenfälle erwartet, an der Küste von Karnataka mäßige bis heftige Regenfälle. In Maharashtra, einschließlich Mumbai, wird der Regen etwas schwächer. #Monsun2025 #Monsun #WetterUpdate #Wettervorhersage #SkymetWeather #Skymet #Wetter

snippet.title: प्रेमिका बनना आसान है पर बीवी बनाना उतना ही मुश्किल है - Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen - Biwi No.1
snippet.description:
► Click here to Subscribe the channel : https://bit.ly/3HS054l 

प्रेमिका बनना आसान है पर बीवी बनाना उतना ही मुश्किल है - Salman Khan, Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen ज़बरदस्त सीन - Biwi No.1 - Hindi ज़बरदस्त सीन

Get ready for a rollercoaster of emotions with Biwi No.1 (1999), a delightful comedy directed by David Dhawan. This film features an ensemble cast including Salman Khan, Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen, Anil Kapoor, and Tabu, delivering a perfect blend of humor and drama.

The story revolves around Prem (Salman Khan), a wealthy man leading a blissful life with his wife Pooja (Karisma Kapoor) and their two children. Their idyllic existence is disrupted when Prem becomes infatuated with Rupali (Sushmita Sen), a glamorous model. As Prem's extramarital affair unfolds, Pooja discovers the betrayal and, with the help of her supportive family and friends, devises a plan to win back her husband and restore her family's happiness. The narrative explores themes of love, trust, and the importance of family bonds, all wrapped in a comedic package. 

Biwi No.1 was both a critical and commercial success, becoming the second highest-grossing Hindi film of 1999. The film received several accolades, with Sushmita Sen winning the Filmfare Award for Best Supporting Actress for her portrayal of Rupali. The movie's soundtrack, composed by Anu Malik, also contributed to its widespread popularity. 

Experience the laughter, tears, and ultimate redemption in Biwi No.1 (1999)!

◾ Film :  Biwi No.1 (1999)
◾ Director: David Dhawan
◾ Writers: Kamal Haasan, Rumi Jaffery, Ikram Akhtar
◾ Producers: Vashu Bhagnani
◾ Cast: Salman Khan, Karisma Kapoor, Sushmita Sen, Anil Kapoor, Tabu
◾ Music: Anu Malik
◾ Genre: Comedy, Drama
◾ Language: Hindi

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: ஆடி முதல் வெள்ளி அம்மன் பாடல் |ஆடி வெள்ளி அம்மனுக்கு | Aadi Velli Ammanukku | Aadi Masam Amman Songs
snippet.description:
#AadiVelliAmmanukku #AmmanSongs #AadiMaasam #LREswari #MahanadhiShobana #Veeramanidasan #BhaktiMaalai

The album "Aadi Velli Ammanukku - ஆடி வெள்ளி அம்மனுக்கு" is dedicated to Goddess Amman. This album has 9 songs sung by L.R Eswari, Veeramanidasan, Shakthi Shanmuguraja, Mahanadhi Shobana, P. Susheela, Sakthi Dasan & Shamala Devi.
Music By : Veeramani Kannan, Kanmani Raja, D.V. Ramani, Aravind & Shakti Shanmugaraja
Lyrics By : Mugilan & Shakti Shanmugaraja
Produced By : Unique Recording 

Amman is the South Indian Goddess of Rain. She is the main South Indian mother/goddess in the southern India. Mari is closely associated with the Hindu goddess Parvati and Durga. 
Her festivals are held during the late summer/early autumn season of Aadi throughout Tamil Nadu and Deccan region, the largest being Aadi Thiruvizha. Devotees offer Pongal that is cooked using earthen pots which are made during the festive season. Rituals such as fire walking and mouth or nose piercing are also practised. Mari in Tamil means rain. Thus she is referred to as Mariyayee or Aathaa. Aathaa means mother or grandmother. She symbolizes sacrifice, motherhood, abundant wealth and good health. 

May Goddess Amman Bless You All ! Om Sakthi !

Do Like, Share, Comment & Subscribe to Bhakti Maalai !

தாயை தெய்வமாகக் கருதி வழிபடும் சக்தி வழிபாடு மாரியம்மன் வழிபாடு...
அதுவும் தென்னிந்திய மக்களின் கண்கண்ட தெய்வமாக விளங்குபவள் மாரியம்மன்...
மாரி என்ற சொல்லுக்கு மழை என்பது பொருள்...
கருணையை மழையாகப் பொழிவதால் மாரியம்மன் என்று சக்தி அழைக்கப்படுகின்றாள்...
கோடைக்காலங்களில் ஏற்படும் வெம்மை நோயான அம்மை வெப்ப நோய் முதலியவற்றை தீர்த்து நாடு தழைக்கவும் மண்ணுலக உயிர்களைக் காக்கவும் அருள்புரிகின்ற அன்னையை மாரியாத்தா என்கின்றோம்...
இவளையே பார்வதி,பராசக்தி,மாகாளி,மகமாயி,துர்கை என்றெல்லாம் நாம் போற்றி துதி செய்கின்றோம்...
இவளே சமயபுரத்தில் மாரியம்மனாகவும்,
சத்தியமங்கலத்தில் பண்ணாரியாகவும்,
கோவையில் கோனியம்மனாகவும், 
சேலம் கோட்டைமாரியம்மனாகவும், காசி விசாலாட்சி யாகவும்,காஞ்சிகாமாட்சியாகவும்,மதுரைமீனாட்சியாகவும்,திருவேற்காட்டில் கருமாரியாகவும்,மாங்காட்டில் காமாட்சியாகவும்,புன்னைநல்லூர் மாரியம்மனாகவும்,
மலையனூர் அங்காளபரமேஸ்வரி யாகவும்,மருவத்தூர் ஆதிபராசக்தியாகவும்,
பெரியபாளையம் பவானியம்மனாகவும்
கோவில் கொண்டு உலகை காத்து இரட்சிக்கின்றாள்...
இப்படி எங்கும் சக்தி எதிலும் சக்தி என இருக்கும் அம்பிகை மாரியம்மனுக்கு ஆடிமாதம் திருவிழா வெகுசிறப்பாக் கொண்டாடப்படுகிறது...
பக்தர்கள் அம்மனுக்கு காப்புக் கட்டி விரதமிருந்து மஞ்சள் ஆடை வேம்பாடை தரித்து அலகிட்டு செடலிட்டு கரகம் காவடி எடுத்து தீமிதித்து கூழ் வார்த்து பொங்கலிட்டு காணிக்கை செலுத்தி அம்மனை மனதார வேண்டி வளமான வாழ்வும் நிறைவான செல்வமும் நோயற்ற வாழ்வும் நீண்ட ஆரோக்கியமும் மனம்போம் மாங்கல்யம் மக்கட்பேறு கிடைக்கவும் இந்த ஆடி மாதத்தில் மாரியம்மன் சன்னதி தேடி அலைஅலையாய் மக்கள் கூட்டம் வருவதை காணக்கண்கோடி வேண்டும்...
நாமும் நம் தாய் மாரியம்மனை கைதொழுது மங்களம் பெறுவோம்...
ஓம்சக்தி...பராசக்தி...

சத்தியமங்கலத்தில் பண்ணாரியாகவும்,
கோவையில் கோனியம்மனாகவும், 
சேலம் கோட்டைமாரியம்மனாகவும், காசி விசாலாட்சி யாகவும்,காஞ்சிகாமாட்சியாகவும்,மதுரைமீனாட்சியாகவும்,திருவேற்காட்டில் கருமாரியாகவும்,மாங்காட்டில் காமாட்சியாகவும்,புன்னைநல்லூர் மாரியம்மனாகவும்,
மலையனூர் அங்காளபரமேஸ்வரி யாகவும்,மருவத்தூர் ஆதிபராசக்தியாகவும்,
பெரியபாளையம் பவானியம்மனாகவும்
கோவில் கொண்டு உலகை காத்து இரட்சிக்கின்றாள்...
இப்படி எங்கும் சக்தி எதிலும் சக்தி என இருக்கும் அம்பிகை மாரியம்மனுக்கு ஆடிமாதம் திருவிழா வெகுசிறப்பாக் கொண்டாடப்படுகிறது...
பக்தர்கள் அம்மனுக்கு காப்புக் கட்டி விரதமிருந்து மஞ்சள் ஆடை வேம்பாடை தரித்து அலகிட்டு செடலிட்டு கரகம் காவடி எடுத்து தீமிதித்து கூழ் வார்த்து பொங்கலிட்டு காணிக்கை செலுத்தி அம்மனை மனதார வேண்டி வளமான வாழ்வும் நிறைவான செல்வமும் நோயற்ற வாழ்வும் நீண்ட ஆரோக்கியமும் மனம்போம் மாங்கல்யம் மக்கட்பேறு கிடைக்கவும் இந்த ஆடி மாதத்தில் மாரியம்மன் சன்னதி தேடி அலைஅலையாய் மக்கள் கூட்டம் வருவதை காணக்கண்கோடி வேண்டும்...
நாமும் நம் தாய் மாரியம்மனை கைதொழுது மங்களம் பெறுவோம்...
ஓம்சக்தி...பராசக்தி...

snippet.title: Mere Murshid Mere Yaara | Sarzameen | Prithviraj S, Kajol, Ibrahim Ali Khan, Vishal Mishra, Jaani
snippet.description:
Mere Murshid Mere Yaara is a heartfelt qawwali-inspired love song, beautifully sung by Vishal Mishra and Salman Ali.

Releasing July 25, only on JioHotstar!  

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Song: Mere Murshid Mere Yaara  
Album: Sarzameen
Singer: Vishal Mishra, Salman Ali
Music Director: Vishal Mishra
Lyricist: Jaani
Featuring Starcast: Kajol, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Ibrahim Ali Khan

Music Arranged & Produced by: Vishal Mishra
Music Assistants: Kumar Gaurav Singh, Trihangku Lahkar, Bitupon Boruah
Recorded, Mixed & Mastered by: Vijay Dayal @ YRF Studio
Special Thanks: Azeem Dayani
Strokes: Tapas Roy
Guitar & Bass: Rhythm Shaw
Keys & Harmonium: Vishal Mishra
Chorus / Qawali: Vivek Naik, Sagar Lele, Umesh Joshi, Santosh Bote, Mangesh Shirke, Mohan Morajkar, Anil Bhilare, Yashad Ghanekar, Siddhant Karawde, Karan Kaagle, Vidit Patankar
Live Rhythms Arranged by: Prashant Sonagra, Swaranjay Dhumal
Tabla: Prashant Sonagra & Navin Sharma
Dholak: Swaranjay Dhumal, Navin Sharma, Ishtiyaq Khan, Mushtaq Khan
Ghungroo Tabla: Shankar Kamble
Percussion: Swaranjay Dhumal, Prashant Sonagra

Lyrics:
Yaaron Ka yaar Hai…. 
Madadgar Parwardigaara… 
Mere Yaar Nu Sajdaaa Karke.. 
Ohde Naam di Eid Guzaraaa…..

Tum mile ho iss tarah se 
Jaise Maula mil gaya ho 
Mile Badal Mili Nadiyaan 
Mila Sukoon…

Meri Aankhon ke rasto se 
Bann gaya saans tu meri Aur phir 
Saanso se hoke 
Bann gaya khoon..

Dil ka Dariya Chalkeeee… 
Rab Hai Aaya chal kee..
Tu Dariya Hai Mai hoon 
Saahil Tera Hoga na..

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Mai Tuteya Taara 
Mere peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaa… Bakhudaa..

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Main Tuteya Taara 
Mere Ali ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaa… Bakhudaa..

Re Ga Ga Ga.. Re Ga Ga Ga.. 
Re Ga Ga .. Re Ga Ga.. Re Ga.. 
Re Ga Ga Ga.. Re Ga Ga Ga.. 
Re Ga Ma Pa.. Ma Ga Re Sa..

Dha Sa Sa Sa.. Dha Sa Sa Sa.. 
Dha Sa Sa.. Dha Sa Sa.. Dha Sa 
Dha Sa Sa Sa.. Dha Sa Sa Sa.. 
Dha Sa Re Ga Re Sa Dha Pa..

Aaa..Aaa…
 
Kitne he Baandhein Hai 
Dhaage re Mazaro Pe.. 
Mere liye tune
Yeh toh bata..

Apne Liye Tune.. 
Kuch Nahi Manga Hai
Mere liye Maangi Har dua 
Meri Maut thi aayi Ishq Mere
Meri Jaan bachayi Ishq Tere

Meri Khaatir Tune Teri Meri 
Khaatir Tune Teri 
Khushiyon Ko Hai Maara.

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Mai Tuteya Taara 
Mere peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaa… Bakhudaa..

Main Ik nadi sa haan
Ik Nadi Sa Tu Hain Naseeb ka Jharna

Tere Gale se Lag ke O sai 
Pairon pe tere hai marna 
Tujh Ko Meri ho jo Aarzoo 
Toh Dauda Chala Aau main. 
Itni Dua na kar iss tarah
Ki Rab Khud na bann jau mai

Ab kya kahu ke mere Huzoor 
Har Har Nafaz mai bas tu hai
Meri Arzoo mai.. meri bandagi mai.. 
Bas tu hai.. tu hai..bas tu hai

Iss Ishq ki na Intehaan
Ab kya kahu ki mere huzoor
 
Tu Dariya hai Mai hoon Paani 
Tu Dariya hai Mai hoon Paani 
Dariya ka hoon Maara…

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Mai Tuteya Taara 
Mere peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaa… Bakhudaa..

Mere Murshid Mere Yaara 
Tu Chann Main Tuteya Taara 
Mere Peer ka tu hai Ishara 
Bakhudaa… Bakhudaa..

snippet.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Innovation powered by you in every mode. The Club is Yours in FC 26, launching September 26. Pre-order now: http://x.ea.com/84657

Play your way with an overhauled gameplay experience, Manager Live Challenges that bring fresh storylines to the new season, and Archetypes inspired by greats of the game. http://x.ea.com/84762

Pre-order EA SPORTS FC 26™ Ultimate Edition by August 26 to receive:
An untradeable ICON Player Item at launch. 
Automatic upgrade to a Champion ICON later in the season.

EA SPORTS FC 25™ players will also receive:
An exclusive EVO that boosts any player’s shooting to 99.
Pick 1 of 5 untradeable ICON players rated 93+ from previous campaigns including Grassroot Greats, FUT Birthday, Dreamchasers & FUT Immortals in EA SPORTS FC™ 25. 

Pre-order EA SPORTS FC 26™ Ultimate Edition to receive:
Up to 7 days early access
6000 FC Points over 2 months (4500 FC Points over 2 months for Nintendo Switch)
Additional Football Ultimate Team™ Player Evolution Slot
Season 1 Premium Pass


Subscribe to see more from EA SPORTS FC™: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

#EASPORTSFC #FC26

ja.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | 公式公開トレーラー
ja.description:
皆さんの声に応え、全ゲームモードを一新9月26日に発売されるFC 26では、クラブはあなたのもの今すぐ予約: http://x.ea.com/84657

一新されたゲームプレイ体験、新シーズンに新たなストーリーをもたらす監督ライブチャレンジ、そして偉大な選手をモチーフにしたアーキタイプで思いのままにプレイできます。http://x.ea.com/84762

8月26日までにEA SPORTS FC™ 26 Ultimate Editionを予約した方向けの特典：
ローンチ時に入手できるアイコン選手アイテム（トレード不可）
後日シーズン中にチャンピオンアイコンに自動でアップグレード

EA SPORTS FC 25™をプレイした方向けの特典：
任意の選手のシュートを99に強化する限定EVO
EA SPORTS FC™ 25の過去のキャンペーンから、レート93以上のグラスルーツ・グレート、FUTバースデー、ドリームチェイサーズ、FUTイモータルズのアイコン選手（トレード不可）5名のうち1名を選択可能。

登録してEA SPORTS FC™の詳細をチェック：http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

es-MX.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Tráiler oficial de revelación
es-MX.description:
Innovación basada en tus comentarios en todos los modos. El Club es Tuyo en FC 26, disponible el 26 de septiembre. Reserva ahora: http://x.ea.com/84657

Juega a tu manera con una experiencia de juego mejorada, desafíos de DT en vivo que suman más historias a la nueva temporada y arquetipos inspirados en las máximas estrellas de la historia del futbol. http://x.ea.com/84762

Reserva EA SPORTS FC 26™ Ultimate Edition antes del 26 de agosto y recibe:
Un item de futbolista ÍCONO intransferible en el lanzamiento. 
Una mejora automática a ÍCONO de Campeón más adelante en la temporada.

Si juegas EA SPORTS FC 25™, también recibirás:
Una EVO exclusiva que potencia los tiros de cualquier futbolista a 99.
Elige 1 de 5 futbolistas ÍCONOS intransferibles con GLB de 93+ de campañas anteriores en EA SPORTS FC™ 25, incluyendo Grandes de bases, Cumpleaños de FUT, Buscasueños e Inmortales de FUT. 

Suscríbete para ver más de EA SPORTS FC™: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

ko.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | 공식 공개 트레일러
ko.description:
모든 모드에서 여러분이 이끄는 혁신. 'The Club is Yours', 9월 26일 FC 26가 출시됩니다. 지금 예약 구매: http://x.ea.com/84657

개선된 게임플레이, 새로운 시즌에 새로운 스토리라인을 제공하는 감독 라이브 챌린지, 위대한 선수들에게 영감을 받은 유형으로 여러분이 원하는 방식으로 플레이하세요. http://x.ea.com/84762

8월 26일까지 EA SPORTS FC™ 26 Ultimate Edition 예약 구매* 시 혜택:
출시 시 거래 불가 아이콘 선수 아이템. 
시즌 후반부에 챔피언 아이콘으로 자동 업그레이드.

EA SPORTS FC™ 25 플레이어 혜택:
선수의 슈팅을 99까지 높여 주는 특별 진화.
EA SPORTS FC™ 25의 풀뿌리 위대한 선수, FUT 생일, 드림체이서, FUT 불멸자를 포함하여 이전 캠페인에서 93+ 등급의 거래 불가 아이콘 선수 5명 중 1명을 선택하세요. 

구독하고 EA SPORTS FC™에 대해 더 알아보세요: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

pl.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Oficjalny zwiastun premiery
pl.description:
Innowacja we wszystkich trybach. Klub należy do Ciebie w grze FC 26, która będzie dostępna 26 września. Zamów w przedsprzedaży już teraz: http://x.ea.com/84657

Zaprojektowaliśmy rozgrywkę od podstaw, przygotowaliśmy wyzwania menedżerskie na żywo, które wprowadzą świeżą fabułę w nowym sezonie, a także dodaliśmy archetypy inspirowane Wielkimi nazwiskami. http://x.ea.com/84762

Zamów w przedsprzedaży Edycję Ultimate EA SPORTS FC™ 26 do 26 sierpnia, a otrzymasz:
Niewymienną kartę IKONY w dniu premiery. 
Automatyczne ulepszenie IKONY mistrza na dalszym etapie sezonu.

Gracze EA SPORTS FC 25™ otrzymają również:
Specjalną kartę ewolucji ulepszającą poziom strzelania dowolnego piłkarza lub piłkarki do 99.
Wybierz 1 z 5 niewymiennych kart IKON o ocenie 93+ z poprzednich kampanii EA SPORTS FC™ 25 takich jak Lokalne Gwiazdy, Urodziny FUT, Łowcy marzeń oraz Nieśmiertelni FUT. 

Zasubskrybuj, aby dowiedzieć się więcej o EA SPORTS FC™: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

ar.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | الفيديو دعائي الرسمي للكشف عن اللعبة
ar.description:
الابتكار المدعم بواسطتكم في كل نمط. النادي بين يديك في FC 26، سيتم إصدارها في 26 سبتمبر. اطلب مسبقاً الآن: http://x.ea.com/84657

العب بأسلوبك مع تجربة بيئة اللعب المجدّدة، وتحديات المدير الفني المباشرة التي تجلب قصصاً جديدة إلى الموسم الجديد والأنماط النموذجية المستلهمة من عظماء اللعبة. http://x.ea.com/84762

اطلب مسبقاً إصدار EA SPORTS FC 26™ Ultimate Edition بحلول 26 أغسطس للحصول على:
عنصر لاعب أيقونة ليس للمقايضة عند الإصدار. 
ترقية تلقائية إلى أيقونة بطل في وقت لاحق من الموسم.

سيتلقى لاعبو EA SPORTS FC 25™‎ أيضاً:
ارتقاء حصري يعزّز تسديد أي لاعب إلى 99.
اختر 1 من 5 لاعبين أيقونات ليسوا للمقايضة بإجمالي 93+ من الحملات السابقة، بما في ذلك، العظماء الشعبيون، وعيد ميلاد FUT، والحالمون، والخالدون في FUT في EA SPORTS FC™ 25. 

اشترك لمشاهدة المزيد من EA SPORTS FC™‎‏: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

Impulsa la innovación en cada modo de juego. El club es tuyo en FC 26, disponible el 26 de septiembre. Resérvalo ya: http://x.ea.com/84657

Juega a tu manera con una experiencia de juego renovada, desafíos de Mánager en vivo que traen historias originales a la nueva temporada y arquetipos inspirados en grandes del deporte. http://x.ea.com/84762

Reserva EA SPORTS FC™ 26 Ultimate Edition antes del 26 de agosto para recibir:
Un artículo de futbolista ICONO intransferible en el lanzamiento. 
Mejora automática a ICONO de Campeón más adelante en la temporada.

Quienes jueguen a EA SPORTS FC 25™ también recibirán:
Una EVO exclusiva que aumenta el tiro de cualquier futbolista a 99.
Elección de 1 de 5 futbolistas ICONO intransferibles con GRL 93+ de campañas anteriores, incluyendo Grandes bases, Aniversario de FUT, Cazasueños e Inmortales de FUT en EA SPORTS FC™ 25. 

Suscríbete para saber más de EA SPORTS FC™: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

it.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Trailer di presentazione ufficiale
it.description:

Gioca a modo tuo con un'esperienza di gioco migliorata, le sfide Tecnico live che offrono storie inedite nella nuova stagione e archetipi ispirati ai grandi del calcio. http://x.ea.com/84762

un oggetto giocatore ICONA non scambiabile all'uscita.

de.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Offizieller Enthüllungstrailer
de.description:
Von der Community inspirierte Innovationen in allen Modi. The Club is Yours. FC 26 erscheint am 26. September. Jetzt vorbestellen: http://x.ea.com/84657

Spiele, wie du es willst – mit überarbeitetem Gameplay, Live-Management-Challenges für frische Storys in der neuen Saison und auf den Besten des Fußballs basierenden Archetypen. http://x.ea.com/84762

Bestelle die EA SPORTS FC™ 26 Ultimate Edition bis 26. September vor und erhalte:
Ein untauschbares ICON-Profi-Item beim Launch. 
Automatisches Upgrade auf ein Champion-ICON im weiteren Saisonverlauf.

Wer EA SPORTS FC™ 25 spielt, erhält außerdem:
Eine exklusive EVO, die den Schusswert eines beliebigen Profis auf 99 erhöht.
Wähle 1 von 5 untauschbaren ICON-Profis mit 93+ aus früheren Kampagnen, darunter Grassroot Greats, FUT Birthday, Dreamchasers & FUT Immortals in EA SPORTS FC™ 25. 

Abonniere für mehr Infos zu EA SPORTS FC™: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

tr.title: EA SPORTS FC 26 | Resmi Tanıtım Fragmanı
tr.description:
Her modda sizden güç alan yenilik. FC 26’da Kulüp Sizin, 26 Eylül’de çıkıyor. Hemen ön sipariş verin: http://x.ea.com/84657

Yenilenen oynanış deneyimi, yeni sezona yeni hikayeler getiren Teknik Direktör Canlı Meydan Okumaları ve oyunun en büyüklerinden ilham alan Modeller ile istediğiniz gibi oynayın. http://x.ea.com/84762

26 Ağustos’a kadar EA SPORTS FC™ 26 Ultimate Sürüm ön siparişi verin, şunları elde edin:
Lansmanda satılamayan bir İKON Oyuncu Ögesi. 
Sezonun devamında bir Şampiyon İKONA gelecek otomatik yükseltme.

EA SPORTS FC 25™ oyuncuları şunları da elde edecek:
Herhangi bir oyuncunun şutunu 99’a yükselten özel bir Geliştirme.
EA SPORTS FC™ 25’ten Altyapı Harikaları, FUT Doğum Günü, Hayalin Peşindekiler ve FUT Ölümsüzler dahil önceki kampanyalardan 93+ reytingli 5 satılamayan İKON oyuncudan 1’inin seçimi. 

EA SPORTS FC™’den daha fazlasını görmek için abone olun: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 4452- Jethalal ke Account se Kaha Gaye 25 लाख रुपए? | Taarak Mehta ka Ooltah Chashmah
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. 

Are you ready for the challenge? 
Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  
#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu)

Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide

Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha

pt-BR.description:
Isso se tornou um grande problema para nós, malaialas, agora. O que devemos fazer? Compartilhe... Que seja útil.
0:00 Óleo de coco 500 por quilo.
1:53 Qual óleo devemos usar?
3:25 Por que óleo de coco?
4:12 Não devemos comer óleo de girassol?
5:50 Óleo de palma funciona?
8:19 Como tornar o óleo de palma saudável?
9:00 Não cozinhe em azeite de oliva.
10:40 O que é melhor para a saúde?
Para agendamentos, ligue para 90 6161 5959.

---------------------------------------------------
O Dr. N S Rajesh Kumar é médico homeopata e nutricionista em Pettah, Thiruvananthapuram, e tem 20 anos de experiência na área. Ele concluiu o Bacharelado em Medicina Homeopática (BHMS) pela Faculdade de Medicina Homeopática Dr. Padiyar Memorial, Ernakulam, em 2003, e Nutrição Clínica pela Faculdade de Medicina de Trivandrum.

Ele é o Médico Homeopata Chefe do Departamento de Homeopatia, Medicina Holística e Pesquisa do Estresse do Instituto de Medicina da Faculdade de Thiruvananthapuram. Alguns dos serviços oferecidos pelo médico incluem: Controle do Diabetes, Aconselhamento Dietético, Tratamento da Queda de Cabelo, Gestão do Estilo de Vida, Pressão Arterial, Colesterol, Aconselhamento Dietético para Perda de Peso, Tratamento de Doenças Hepáticas, etc.

fr-FR.title: L'huile de coco coûte 500 $ le kilo. Faut-il acheter de l'huile de palme ou de l'huile de tournes...
fr-FR.description:
C'est devenu un gros problème pour nous, les Malayalis. Que faire ? Partager… Que cela soit utile.
0:00 Huile de coco : 500 g par kilo
1:53 Quelle huile utiliser ?
3:25 Pourquoi l'huile de coco ?
4:12 Faut-il éviter l'huile de tournesol ?
5:50 L'huile de palme est-elle efficace ?
8:19 Comment rendre l'huile de palme saine ?
9:00 Ne pas cuisiner avec de l'huile d'olive
10:40 Qu'est-ce qui est meilleur pour la santé ?
Pour prendre rendez-vous, veuillez appeler le 90 6161 5959

---------------------------------------------------
Le Dr N. S. Rajesh Kumar est médecin homéopathe et nutritionniste à Pettah, Thiruvananthapuram, et possède 20 ans d'expérience dans ce domaine. Il a obtenu son diplôme de BHMS au Dr Padiyar Memorial Homeopathic Medical College d'Ernakulam en 2003 et un diplôme de nutrition clinique à la faculté de médecine de Trivandrum.

Il est médecin homéopathe en chef du service de l'Institut de recherche sur l'homéopathie, la médecine holistique et le stress de la faculté de médecine de Thiruvananthapuram. Parmi ses services, on peut citer : la gestion du diabète, les conseils diététiques, le traitement de la chute des cheveux, la gestion du mode de vie, la prise en charge de la tension artérielle, du cholestérol, des régimes amaigrissants et des maladies du foie.

hi.title: नारियल तेल 500 रुपये किलो है.. अब पाम ऑयल खरीदें या सूरजमुखी का? सेहत के लिए कौन सा ज़्यादा बेहतर...
hi.description:
यह अब हम मलयाली लोगों के लिए एक बड़ी समस्या बन गई है। हमें क्या करना चाहिए? साझा करें। इसे उपयोगी बनाएँ।
0:00 नारियल तेल 500 प्रति किलो
1:53 हमें कौन सा तेल इस्तेमाल करना चाहिए?
3:25 नारियल तेल क्यों?
4:12 क्या हमें सूरजमुखी का तेल नहीं खाना चाहिए?
5:50 क्या ताड़ का तेल काम करेगा?
8:19 ताड़ के तेल को स्वास्थ्यवर्धक कैसे बनाएँ?
9:00 जैतून के तेल में खाना न पकाएँ
10:40 स्वास्थ्य के लिए कौन सा बेहतर है?
अपॉइंटमेंट के लिए कृपया 90 6161 5959 पर कॉल करें।

---------------------------------------------------
डॉ. एन. एस. राजेश कुमार, तिरुवनंतपुरम के पेट्टा में एक होम्योपैथिक चिकित्सक और पोषण विशेषज्ञ हैं और उन्हें इस क्षेत्र में 20 वर्षों का अनुभव है। उन्होंने 2003 में डॉ. पडियार मेमोरियल होम्योपैथिक मेडिकल कॉलेज, एर्नाकुलम से बीएचएमएस और मेडिकल कॉलेज, त्रिवेंद्रम से क्लिनिकल न्यूट्रिशन की डिग्री प्राप्त की है।

वह होम्योपैथिक, समग्र चिकित्सा एवं तनाव अनुसंधान संस्थान, मेडिकल कॉलेज, तिरुवनंतपुरम के मुख्य होम्योपैथिक चिकित्सक विभाग हैं। डॉक्टर द्वारा प्रदान की जाने वाली कुछ सेवाएँ इस प्रकार हैं: मधुमेह प्रबंधन, आहार परामर्श, बालों के झड़ने का उपचार, जीवनशैली प्रबंधन, रक्तचाप, कोलेस्ट्रॉल, वजन घटाने के लिए आहार परामर्श और यकृत रोग उपचार आदि।

it.title: L'olio di cocco costa 500 al chilo. Ora, dovresti comprare olio di palma o di girasole? Qual è il...
it.description:
Questo è diventato un grosso problema per noi malayali... Cosa dovremmo fare? Condividi... Lascia che sia utile
0:00 Olio di cocco 500 al chilo
1:53 Quale olio dovremmo usare?
3:25 Perché l'olio di cocco?
4:12 Non dovremmo mangiare olio di girasole?
5:50 L'olio di palma funziona?
8:19 Come rendere l'olio di palma sano?
9:00 Non cucinare in olio d'oliva
10:40 Qual è il migliore per la salute?
Per appuntamenti, chiamare il numero 90 6161 5959

---------------------------------------------------
Il Dott. N S Rajesh Kumar è un medico omeopatico e nutrizionista a Pettah, Thiruvananthapuram e vanta 20 anni di esperienza in questo campo. Ha conseguito la laurea in Medicina Omeopatica (BHMS) presso il Dr. Padiyar Memorial Homeopathic Medical College di Ernakulam nel 2003 e la specializzazione in Nutrizione Clinica presso la Facoltà di Medicina di Trivandrum.

È il Direttore del Dipartimento di Medicina Omeopatica presso l'Istituto di Ricerca Omeopatica, Olistica e sullo Stress della Facoltà di Medicina di Thiruvananthapuram. Tra i servizi offerti dal medico figurano: gestione del diabete, consulenza dietetica, trattamento della caduta dei capelli, gestione dello stile di vita, controllo della pressione sanguigna, colesterolo, consulenza dietetica per la perdita di peso e trattamento delle malattie epatiche, ecc.

snippet.title: ஆடி வருகுதே அம்மா | ஆடி மாதம் 2025 அம்மன் பாடல்க‌ள் | Aadi Varuguthea Amma | L R Eswari | Aadi Masam
snippet.description:
#AadiVarugutheaAmma #AmmanSongs #Veeramanidasan #LREswari #mahanadhishobana #shakthishanmugaraja 

The album " Aadi Varuguthea Amma - ஆடி வருகுதே அம்மா " is dedicated to Goddess Amman. This album has 9 songs sung by L.R Eswari, Shakthi Shanmugaraja, Veeramanidasan, Mahanadhi Shobana, P. Susheela, S Janaki, Bombay Saradha, Sakthi Dasan  
Lyrics By : Mugilan, Bharathi Ganesh & Shakthi Shanmugaraja
Music By : Kanmani Raja, D.V.Ramani & Shakthi Shanmugaraja
Produced By : Unique Recording

Amman is the South Indian Goddess of Rain. She is the main South Indian mother/goddess in the southern India. Mari is closely associated with the Hindu goddess Parvati and Durga. 
Her festivals are held during the late summer/early autumn season of Aadi throughout Tamil Nadu and Deccan region, the largest being Aadi Thiruvizha. Devotees offer Pongal that is cooked using earthen pots which are made during the festive season. Rituals such as fire walking and mouth or nose piercing are also practised. Mari in Tamil means rain. Thus she is referred to as Mariyayee or Aathaa. Aathaa means mother or grandmother. She symbolizes sacrifice, motherhood, abundant wealth and good health. 

May Goddess Amman Bless You All ! Om Sakthi !

Do Like, Share, Comment & Subscribe to Bhakti Maalai !

தாயை தெய்வமாகக் கருதி வழிபடும் சக்தி வழிபாடு மாரியம்மன் வழிபாடு...
அதுவும் தென்னிந்திய மக்களின் கண்கண்ட தெய்வமாக விளங்குபவள் மாரியம்மன்...
மாரி என்ற சொல்லுக்கு மழை என்பது பொருள்...
கருணையை மழையாகப் பொழிவதால் மாரியம்மன் என்று சக்தி அழைக்கப்படுகின்றாள்...
கோடைக்காலங்களில் ஏற்படும் வெம்மை நோயான அம்மை வெப்ப நோய் முதலியவற்றை தீர்த்து நாடு தழைக்கவும் மண்ணுலக உயிர்களைக் காக்கவும் அருள்புரிகின்ற அன்னையை மாரியாத்தா என்கின்றோம்...
இவளையே பார்வதி,பராசக்தி,மாகாளி,மகமாயி,துர்கை என்றெல்லாம் நாம் போற்றி துதி செய்கின்றோம்...
இவளே சமயபுரத்தில் மாரியம்மனாகவும்,
சத்தியமங்கலத்தில் பண்ணாரியாகவும்,
கோவையில் கோனியம்மனாகவும், 
சேலம் கோட்டைமாரியம்மனாகவும், காசி விசாலாட்சி யாகவும்,காஞ்சிகாமாட்சியாகவும்,மதுரைமீனாட்சியாகவும்,திருவேற்காட்டில் கருமாரியாகவும்,மாங்காட்டில் காமாட்சியாகவும்,புன்னைநல்லூர் மாரியம்மனாகவும்,
மலையனூர் அங்காளபரமேஸ்வரி யாகவும்,மருவத்தூர் ஆதிபராசக்தியாகவும்,
பெரியபாளையம் பவானியம்மனாகவும்
கோவில் கொண்டு உலகை காத்து இரட்சிக்கின்றாள்...
இப்படி எங்கும் சக்தி எதிலும் சக்தி என இருக்கும் அம்பிகை மாரியம்மனுக்கு ஆடிமாதம் திருவிழா வெகுசிறப்பாக் கொண்டாடப்படுகிறது...
பக்தர்கள் அம்மனுக்கு காப்புக் கட்டி விரதமிருந்து மஞ்சள் ஆடை வேம்பாடை தரித்து அலகிட்டு செடலிட்டு கரகம் காவடி எடுத்து தீமிதித்து கூழ் வார்த்து பொங்கலிட்டு காணிக்கை செலுத்தி அம்மனை மனதார வேண்டி வளமான வாழ்வும் நிறைவான செல்வமும் நோயற்ற வாழ்வும் நீண்ட ஆரோக்கியமும் மனம்போம் மாங்கல்யம் மக்கட்பேறு கிடைக்கவும் இந்த ஆடி மாதத்தில் மாரியம்மன் சன்னதி தேடி அலைஅலையாய் மக்கள் கூட்டம் வருவதை காணக்கண்கோடி வேண்டும்...
நாமும் நம் தாய் மாரியம்மனை கைதொழுது மங்களம் பெறுவோம்...
ஓம்சக்தி...பராசக்தி...

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: Teri Galiyon Mein (Official Video) Javed-Mohsin | Mohammad Faiz | Sanika Bhoite | Danish Sabri
snippet.description:
Mohabbat bhi wahi. Galti bhi wahi aur tabaahi bhi.

Get ready to feel every beat of heartbreak with the official video of “Teri Galiyon Mein” – a soulful tale of love, loss, and longing.

Sung by the sensational Mohammad Faiz, composed by the hitmaker duo Javed-Mohsin, and penned by the lyrical genius Danish Sabri – this one’s going to stay with you long after it ends.

Featuring the stunning Sanika Bhoite, the video narrates a a story that will tug at your heart strings. 

#TeriGaliyonMein #MohammadFaiz

Featuring the stunning Sanika Bhoite. 

🎧  Audio Credits

➟ Music composer : Javed-Mohsin
➟ Singer : Mohammad Faiz 
➟ Sufi  vocals by - Danish sabri 
➟ Lyrics by - Danish sabri 

➟ Music team :

➟ Original soundtrack theme written and composed by : Javed-Mohsin 

➟ Music produced by : Jackie Vanjari
➟ All live guitars played by : Shomu seal 
➟ Solo  violin played by : Jitender Thakur 
➟ Live sarangi played by : Muddasar Ali khan 
➟ Indian rhythm ( Tabla & dholak ) by : Raju Sardar and team , firoz khan , sanjeev sen , Zuber hussain Warsi , Tahir Hasan
➟ Percussions and side rhythm played by : Satyajit Jamsandekar
➟ Live strings played by : Prakash verma , Sunil Verma , Jitender Jawda , Shyam jawda , Prabhat kishore , sandeep thakur , dilip Bose , Mahendra Bedi , chandan singh , raju padhiyar , dilip Bose 
➟ Live strokes played by : Tapas Roy
➟ Solo Trumpet played by : Kishore Soda 
➟ Backup qawali vocals by - Sameer khan royal , Aman khan , Harshad Munir & khalid Iqbal 
➟ Song recorded @Studio 504 by : Rahul M sharma 
➟ Javed-Mohsin’s legal advisor : Rohini Vakil 
➟ Assistant Mix engineer - Michael Edwin Pillai 
➟ Mixed & Mastered by : Eric Pillai @FSOB

🎬 Video Credits

➟ Director - Sneha Shetty Kohli 
➟ Starring - Sanika Bhoite & Mohammad Faiz
➟ DOP - Girish Kant
➟ Line producer - Karan Dedhia 
➟ 1st Ad - Amitesh Sanghani
➟ Assistant director - Celestine Dcruz
➟ Assistant Costume Stylist - Neha Khub & Dhwani
➟ Associate Dop - Akshay Sarode
➟ Choregrapher - Jayshree Kelkar
➟ Assistant Choreographer -Shwetha j Poojary
➟ Gimbal Opretor -Sumit jaiswal 
➟ Associate Gimbal Operator-Sunny jaiswal 
➟ Costume stylist -Vibhuti Chamaria
➟ Production designer - Rupendra Das 
➟ Hair &Make up - Amit Pawar Diwakar Kadam
➟ Location - Swagat Villa by the pool
➟ Editor - Bunty Nagi
➟ Editing studio - Just Right Studioz
➟ DI - DreamTone Studio
➟ DI Colorist - Prashant B Dhotre
➟ DI Producer - Alpa Thakkar
➟ Casting (Sanika Bhoite) - Ashish Natekar (Big Wave Entertainment)
➟ Faiz hair - Azruddin

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Lyrics:

Mukhda :

Raas na aaya mujhko tujhse dil lagana
Hasti hai yeh duniya mujhko kehke deweena
Yaad rakhega ek din saara yeh zamana
Aankhon mein aansu lekar mera muskurana

Hai mere paas wahi jo gaya hai tu de kar

Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil lekar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa kehkar
Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil lekar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa kehkar

Antra :
Yeh maanta hoon ishq se badhkar koi jaadu tona nahi
Jise tu khel ke tod de yeh dil hai khilona nahi

Yeh maanta hoon ishq se badhkar koi jaadu tona nahi
Jise tu khel ke tod de yeh dil hai khilona nahi

Duayein de rahe hain tujhko saare gham seh kar

Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil le kar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar
Teri galiyon mein phir raha hoon toota dil le kar
Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar

Outro :
Dhoondhne walon ko tu bata de mera pata hai teri galiyon mein
Dard mein dooba dil hai magar jeene ka mazza hai teri galiyon mein

Main hoon woh bejaan mohabaat jiski dawa hai teri galiyon mein
Duniya hai mandir masjid mein mera khuda hai teri galiyon mein

Bewafa ne bhi thukraya bewafa keh kar

snippet.title: Mortal Kombat 2 - Official 'Uncaged Fury' Teaser Trailer (2025) Karl Urban
snippet.description:
Don't miss the 'Uncaged Fury' Teaser Trailer for Mortal Kombat 2, the upcoming action film based on the hit Mortal Kombat game IP distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures. Take a look at the in-universe film trailer for Uncaged Fury starring the one and only Johnny Cage, portrayed by Karl Urban. 

Uncaged Fury sees the legendary Johnny Cage take on a band of goons with ease, making use of pipes, fast-paced combat skills, and an aura unlike any other.

Mortal Kombat 2 is in theaters on October 24.

Keerthi and Raghav decide to spend their anniversary at a 5 star hotel, as they begin to become intimate, Keerthi breaks a news to Raghav which changes the mood of the whole night. 
What did Keerthi say to Raghav? What will happen in the rest of the night? Watch this interesting tamil short film and find out!

snippet.description:
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

snippet.title: AMIT SAINI ROHTAKIYA : Neelkanth (Official Video) Jeetu G | New Haryanavi Bholenath Songs 2025
snippet.description:
White Hill Dhaakad Presents 🔱| New Haryanavi Bholenath Song 2025 |
Neelkanth – Your favourite Amit Saini Rohtakiya is back with a powerful bhakti anthem this Shravan! This Haryanvi devotional track is a tribute to Bhole Baba, laced with divine energy, rustic vocals, and a vibe that’ll resonate through your soul.

Penned by DK Mahla Kapro, composed and sung by Amit Saini Rohtakiya himself, with soul-thumping music by GR Music, and visuals crafted by Jeetu G – this song captures the raw faith and fire of every Bhole devotee during Kaavad season.

🕉️ Whether you're on a Kaavad Yatra or feeling the Mahadev vibe – this one belongs in your bhakti playlist.
